# Cursor Rules for Traderpost (Legacy Fallback)

1. Read `AGENTS.md` first before implementing anything.
2. Use `agent_docs/` for detailed context (`tech_stack.md`, `product_requirements.md`, `testing.md`).
3. Propose a short plan before multi-file changes.
4. Build incrementally and verify after each feature slice.
5. Run `npm run lint` and relevant tests before calling work complete.
6. Keep API keys server-side only; never expose secrets in client code.
